How
===

* Delegate upwards
* Do, Check, Go
* Do, Inform, Go
* Just Do it

----

:data-x: r0
:data-y: r800
:data-rotate-y: 0
:data-rotate-z: 0
:data-scale: 1


Do, Check, Go
=============

* Complex
* Builds confidence
* Still authorising 

----

Do, Inform, Go
==============

* Less complex
* Giving authority
* Still responsible

----

Just Do it
==============

* Giving authority
* Still responsible
* Build trust, if not seen as lazy

.. image:: images/Just-Do-It.jpg

